To reduce manual effort
makes life easier

pitfalls
--------
Time and effort to write scripts

Pareto principle   (20% of sys administration tasks that you perform are responsible for 80% of your work)

disk usage:
    import shutil
    du = shutil.disk_usage("/")
    print(du.free/du.total*100) # shows available free space

cpu usage:
    import psutil
    psutil.cpu_percent(0.1)